  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U kineskom, nambari 80 huitwa <ruby>八十<rp>(</rp><rt>bā shí</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>.</p>\n<p>Brojevi od 81 do 89 sastoji se dodavanjem cifre jedinica (1–9) nakon <ruby>八十<rp>(</rp><rt>bā shí</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> (80).</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Broj</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Kineski</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">80</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>八十<rp>(</rp><rt>bā shí</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">81</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>八十一<rp>(</rp><rt>bā shí yī</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">82</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>八十二<rp>(</rp><rt>bā shí èr</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">83</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>八十三<rp>(</rp><rt>bā shí sān</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">84</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>八十四<rp>(</rp><rt>bā shí sì</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">85</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>八十五<rp>(</rp><rt>bā shí wǔ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">86</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>八十六<rp>(</rp><rt>bā shí liù</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">87</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>八十七<rp>(</rp><rt>bā shí qī</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">88</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>八十八<rp>(</rp><rt>bā shí bā</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">89</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>八十九<rp>(</rp><rt>bā shí jiǔ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>",
